# Observability

- Log in structured form (objects), not long concatenated strings.
- Every request should have `requestId`/correlation id; include it in all logs.
- Don’t log full bodies for sensitive endpoints (auth, payments, uploads).
- On errors, log: message + error object + minimal context (route, requestId, userId if available).
